UReggie Dlamini (36) ugwetshwe yinkantolo ngoLwesithathu emuva kokulahlwa yicala elithinta owesifazane oneminyaka engu-53. Kuthiwa owesifazane wagitsheliswa imoto nguDlamini ngasemgwaqweni uManor Drive eMbilo. Esesemotweni kuthiwa uDlamini washayela imoto yabheka emathuneni. Kuthiwa wafika emathuneni wambopha owesifazane wamdlwengula ephindelela maqede wabaleka nezimpahla zakhe. Okhulumela amaphoyisa esifundazweni uLieutenant-Colonel Thulani Zwane uthe owesifazane waficwa amaphoyisa esaboshelwe esihlahleni emathuneni. Uthe umsolwa wazama ukubaleka kodwa amaphoyisa ambamba. “Kwavulwa icala lokudlwengula esiteshini eMbilo, idokodo ladluliselwa ophikweni oluphenya amacala odlame lomndeni, ukuvikelwa kwezingane nawocansi. Umsolwa uvalelwe esitokisini waze wagwetshwa,” kusho uZwane. Umsolwa ugwetshwe udilikajele ecaleni lokudlwengula, wagwetshwa iminyaka engu-15 kwelokubamba inkunzi.